_sText:
This map has been created by me but 4 things inside the map has been created by uberkirsche such as the cannon's the bookcase door and the destroyable house.

Iam giving credit of this to uberkirsche for it seems the players like the cannon's used in the map as it was tested in a server.

This map is not built for having bots so only human players could be used and it is built for Zombie servers.

There is 4 well hidden teleports and 7teleports that send you directly to death by spikes open for all to see, there is almost no place to hide that is becuase i wanna give the brain eaters a chance to collect some nice brains for a nice meal.

Map built for holding up to 40players that hopefully shall hold sinse my first fualt that occur.

If there is any question about the map so pleas ask away.

Yes i know the map seems to be abit empty but it is built this way and the newer version will become more full...
Prepare for 1-2 more version of this one map depending on complainments and ideas given to me.

Enjoy the map and find the secrets.
